\b 18. Conclusion\b0\line
The Digital Certificate Verification System demonstrates a secure, layered, and maintainable approach to certificate verification. By replacing manual checks with a database-driven solution, the system improves speed, accuracy, and trust. The use of Java, the DAO pattern, and MySQL makes the solution portable and extensible for future enhancements such as a full web interface and QR code integration.\line
